OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774555873
OL,3,CKiller tells police he's 'had a rough
OL,4,Cday' after neighbour reported screams
OL,6,FA killer tells police he's had "a
OL,7,Freally rough day" as they knock on the
OL,8,Fdoor of his flat, where, unknown to
OL,9,Fthem, the body of Reanne Coulson is
OL,10,Fhidden underneath a bed.
OL,12,FA man from Coventry has been found
OL,13,Fguilty of killing a mother-of-two, 33,
OL,14,Fat his flat in Coventry.
OL,16,FPolice were called to Mohammed
OL,17,FDurnion's home on 21 May last year,
OL,18,Fafter neighbours reported hearing
OL,19,Fscreams.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
