PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774555873
OL,3,CKiller tells police he's 'had a rough
OL,4,Cday' after neighbour reported screams
OL,6,FHe answers the door appearing panicked
OL,7,Fand flustered. He shouts, "Please,
OL,8,FI've had a really rough day...
OL,10,F"Please leave me alone".
OL,12,FHe gestures to rubbish, littering the
OL,13,Ffloor of his flat and says, "look at
OL,14,Fmy house" and asks "please go away,
OL,15,Fyou can't come in here".
OL,17,FHe maintains "there's nothing here"
OL,18,Fand slams the door in their face.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
