OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774555873
OL,3,CKiller tells police he's 'had a rough
OL,4,Cday' after neighbour reported screams
OL,6,FWhen police make it inside, they can
OL,7,Fbe heard walking on glass and other
OL,8,Fwaste covering the floor of the flat.
OL,10,FUnmade beds, piles of clothes, and
OL,11,Ffurniture upended can be seen.
OL,13,FDurnion killed Reanne Coulson in his
OL,14,Fflat and claimed she was hidden under
OL,15,Fa mattress while police were searching
OL,16,Fthe flat.
OL,18,FMs Coulson was last seen in Coventry
OL,19,Fthat day after visiting a food bank at
OL,20,FSt Mary and St Benedict Church.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
