FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774555873
OL,3,CKiller tells police he's 'had a rough
OL,4,Cday' after neighbour reported screams
OL,6,FHer body was found more than five
OL,7,Fweeks after she'd been killed by
OL,8,FDurnion at his flat.
OL,10,FHe put her body into a suitcase and
OL,11,Fdrove four miles to Binley Woods where
OL,12,Fhe hid her body in a shallow grave on
OL,13,Fa bridleway.
OL,15,FHer remains were found on 27 June 2025.
OL,17,FDurnion was found guilty of the
OL,18,Fmanslaughter of Ms Coulson, following
OL,19,Fa trial at Warwickshire Justice Centre.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
